there's no "we" in "bike."

17:44.433 --> 17:45.433
I miss Lanny.

17:46.700 --> 17:49.667
Well, I can't speak for Lanny.

17:49.734 --> 17:50.734
Somebody's got to.

17:52.200 --> 17:56.367
But I bet he feels exactly
the same way you do.

17:56.767 --> 17:58.467
Why don't you give him a call?

18:04.934 --> 18:07.834
