Don't say anything.

18:07.900 --> 18:09.433
I wanna talk.

18:09.500 --> 18:11.633
This bike thing was a stupid idea.

18:11.700 --> 18:14.900
We had more fun earning it
than we do having it.

18:15.834 --> 18:19.000
What's the point of being friends
if we're never in the same room?

18:19.767 --> 18:22.433
Uh-huh. Yeah.

18:23.233 --> 18:24.734
You are so right.

18:25.400 --> 18:27.900
You've got such a way with
words, Lanny.

18:28.367 --> 18:29.800
So, we're agreed.

18:29.867 --> 18:33.533
We sell the bike and we use the money
to go into the ostrich business.

18:34.200 --> 18:35.467
See you soon.

18:37.066 --> 18:40.166
